16:50.468 --> 16:51.594
She's just a child.

16:51.678 --> 16:54.055
That's never stopped you before.

16:55.515 --> 16:58.017
Call me when it's done.

17:02.939 --> 17:04.941
[woman speaking indistinctly
over P.A.]

17:09.320 --> 17:10.655
Mon coeur?

17:10.739 --> 17:13.241
Mon coeur? Hey.

17:21.249 --> 17:22.584
Ca va?

17:26.129 --> 17:27.964
[whispers] How are you feeling?

17:44.147 --> 17:46.149
It was Soldier Boy.

17:52.781 --> 17:54.491
Why are you smiling?

17:54.574 --> 17:57.786
