such short notice, Blue Hawk.
- Oh.

19:19.993 --> 19:21.327
A-Train.

19:21.411 --> 19:22.495
[chuckles] Hey.

19:22.579 --> 19:24.372
Big fan.

19:24.455 --> 19:26.249
