19 are dead.

23:19.065 --> 23:22.360
The NYPD and Bureau
of Superhuman Affairs...

23:22.443 --> 23:24.153
♪ ♪

23:26.572 --> 23:27.782
[breathing heavily]

23:31.702 --> 23:33.579
