about the share price

24:51.324 --> 24:54.368
and the EBITDA margins, okay?

24:57.538 --> 24:59.540
- Thank you.
- So much.

25:00.541 --> 25:02.752
Hey. It's me.

25:02.835 --> 25:04.837
Tell me this isn't
who I think it is.

25:04.921 --> 25:06.505
