who you think it is.

25:06.589 --> 25:08.216
[Starlight] Oh, my God.

25:08.299 --> 25:10.176
[sighs] Look, we're coming
up on the site now.

25:10.259 --> 25:11.636
Can your Crime Analytics people
look for him?

25:11.719 --> 25:13.638
I'm on it.
Just be careful, Hughie.

25:13.721 --> 25:15.264
- [siren wailing]
- [urgent chatter]

25:15.348 --> 25:17.516
[helicopter whirring]

25:29.278 --> 25:31.906
Fucking hell.

25:31.989 --> 25:33.032
[Ivy] Hughie.

25:34.283 --> 25:35.576
Ivy.

25:35.660 --> 25:38.287
Hey, uh... [sighs]

25:38.371 --> 25:39.830
Morning, morning.

25:39.914 --> 25:41.999
- Is Vicky here?
- She's on her way.

25:42.083 --> 25:43.918
Didn't you break your arm?

25:44.001 --> 25:46.337
Yeah, um...

25:46.420 --> 25:48.130
Yes. It turns out
it's a bad sprain,

25:48.214 --> 25:50.591
- so I-I'm okay.
I'll see you later.
- Okay.

25:50.675 --> 25:52.677
[embers crackling]

25:54.178 --> 25:55.429
[Geiger counter
clicking rapidly]

26:03.062 --> 26:04.397
[sighs]

26:09.694 --> 26:10.820
Oi.

26:14.073 --> 26:16.075
Still think
he's the Reds' problem?

26:17.118 --> 26:19.203
All right. Easy, mate.

26:19.287 --> 26:20.621
Fuck you.

26:20.705 --> 26:22.164
I'll find him myself.

26:22.248 --> 26:25.835
And what you gonna do
when you find him, eh?

26:27.378 --> 26:29.463
He's well out
of your league, son.

26:31.257 --> 26:32.174
