focus on the job at hand.

26:43.436 --> 26:46.939
Let me help you
with Soldier Boy.

26:47.023 --> 26:49.817
I owe you that much, and then
you don't got to see me no more.

26:49.900 --> 26:51.444
[sighs]

27:00.703 --> 27:02.246
Knowing you,
you already got a lead?

27:02.330 --> 27:05.499
Course I fucking do.
Look at where we are.

27:08.544 --> 27:09.712
The Legend.

27:09.795 --> 27:12.423
Want to bet Soldier Boy
paid him a visit?

27:18.346 --> 27:20.973
- Do you want the other half?
- No. No.

27:21.057 --> 27:23.768
Not right now, thanks.
You were saying?

27:23.851 --> 27:25.936
