we'd have to comb through

27:26.020 --> 27:27.813
every CCTV camera in the city.

27:27.897 --> 27:30.483
It would take a dozen analysts
working double shifts.

27:30.566 --> 27:32.610
Okay, then let's do it.

27:32.693 --> 27:35.112
Where is everyone?

27:35.196 --> 27:37.073
We are everyone.

27:37.156 --> 27:38.491
