"team players."

27:48.376 --> 27:49.835
Can I have that half?

27:49.919 --> 27:51.087
Thank you.

27:52.129 --> 27:54.423
[breathes deeply]

27:54.507 --> 27:56.258
- [♪ Styliztik Jones:
"Hall of Fame"]
- ♪ Ballin' like the greats ♪

27:56.342 --> 27:57.968
