28:04.225 --> 28:05.434
- What you doing here, man?
- [chuckles]

28:07.144 --> 28:09.522
♪ You don't know nothing
if you don't know Bo Jackson ♪

28:09.605 --> 28:11.982
♪ Crashing through defenders
never knowing what happened ♪

28:12.066 --> 28:14.777
♪ Going through tackles like
I'm driving through traffic ♪

28:14.860 --> 28:17.780
