28:30.042 --> 28:31.836
- What's wrong with you?
- Isn't this what you wanted?

28:31.919 --> 28:34.422
For me to use my platform
to help the community, right?

28:34.505 --> 28:36.590
[sighs]

28:38.134 --> 28:39.385
Five minutes.

28:40.761 --> 28:42.138
All right.

28:46.809 --> 28:48.477
- [microphone feedback squeals]
- Sorry, sorry.

28:48.561 --> 28:52.022
It's the metal in my helmet.

28:52.106 --> 28:54.316
[clears throat]

28:54.400 --> 28:55.860
All right.

28:57.069 --> 28:58.571
To, uh, the residents
of Trenton,

28:58.654 --> 29:00.030
thank you for giving me
the opportunity

29:00.114 --> 29:01.407
to speak with you today.

29:01.490 --> 29:03.284
As you know,
superheroes often have to make,

29:03.367 --> 29:05.369
like, uh, split-second decisions

29:05.453 --> 29:07.955
when fighting crime,
a-a-and I apologize

29:08.038 --> 29:10.249
if any of mine have been...

29:10.332 --> 29:13.919
perceived as being... racist.

29:14.003 --> 29:15.921
