29:16.005 --> 29:17.506
Just ask my friends,

29:17.590 --> 29:20.968
many of whom are, uh, are Black,

29:21.051 --> 29:22.178
like A-Train.

29:22.261 --> 29:24.430
I do not see color.

29:24.513 --> 29:27.183
I only see crime.

29:27.266 --> 29:31.395
And as a sign of my commitment
to you all, I am donating

29:31.479 --> 29:34.899
$10,000 to this
community center. Thank you.

29:34.982 --> 29:36.650
