to be i-in Black neighborhoods.

29:48.746 --> 29:50.164
- That-That's not my fault.
- [overlapping chatter]

29:50.247 --> 29:51.832
[A-Train] All right, all right.
No, that's enough here.

29:51.916 --> 29:53.417
We're done here.
