30:19.109 --> 30:20.444
Hey, Blue Hawk!

30:20.528 --> 30:22.363
[Blue Hawk] Shut the fuck up!

30:22.446 --> 30:23.906
- Fuck out of here!
- [screaming, clamoring]

30:26.450 --> 30:28.494
- Shit!
- Stupid fucks!

30:28.577 --> 30:30.746
Shut the f...
Get the fuck out of here!

30:30.829 --> 30:32.540
- [clamoring]
- [woman crying]

30:32.623 --> 30:33.749
Stop!

30:35.167 --> 30:36.877
[woman] Oh, my God!

30:39.588 --> 30:41.298
[woman crying] Why?!

30:42.341 --> 30:44.176
Nate?

30:45.719 --> 30:46.720
