30:48.305 --> 30:49.223
[knock on door]

30:49.306 --> 30:50.891
[Legend] Just leave it.

30:50.975 --> 30:52.393
What?

30:52.476 --> 30:55.563
Leave the goddamn
clams casino at the door.

30:55.646 --> 30:57.982
