Read a fucking book, kid.

31:17.918 --> 31:20.588
This... this is The Legend.

31:20.671 --> 31:23.007
That's, uh, quite a nickname.

31:23.090 --> 31:26.260
No, it's not a name.
It's a level.

31:26.343 --> 31:28.596
Legend, we need to talk.

31:28.679 --> 31:31.056
- Not him.
- [Mother's Milk] He'll behave.

31:31.140 --> 31:32.391
