47:39.524 --> 47:41.484
- You like that?
- Yeah.

47:41.568 --> 47:43.486
♪ Now they play
little cymbals...

47:43.570 --> 47:44.862
You want it?

47:44.946 --> 47:48.116
- I'm ready.
- [exhales]

47:48.199 --> 47:50.994
♪ It's time to take a stand
for what evolved into man...

47:51.077 --> 47:54.914
Get that spandex down and start
popping those things in there.

47:54.998 --> 47:56.124
- Yeah.
- [clattering]

47:56.207 --> 47:57.750
What the fuck?!

47:57.834 --> 47:59.294
- Oh, no!
- [Crimson Countess shouts]

47:59.377 --> 48:01.004
- What the hell?!
- [rhythmic sloshing continues]

48:01.087 --> 48:03.590
[grunts] Where'd you go?
I'm almost...

48:03.673 --> 48:06.384
[shouting]

48:06.467 --> 48:09.554
[groaning, sighing]

48:10.847 --> 48:12.056
Hello?

48:21.733 --> 48:24.527
Probably not the dom-sub rumble
you fancied tonight, yeah?

48:24.611 --> 48:26.779
What the fuck's up with him?

48:26.863 --> 48:28.823
We ain't here to hurt you.

48:28.906 --> 48:30.450
But I am gonna
tell you something,

48:30.533 --> 48:33.494
and I don't want you
to lose your shit.

48:33.578 --> 48:35.121
What?

48:35.204 --> 48:37.373
Your lover boy's
on his way here.

48:40.126 --> 48:42.128
Soldier Boy.

48:42.211 --> 48:43.504
He's alive.

48:50.845 --> 48:52.680
How'd he escape from Russia?

48:54.223 --> 48:56.934
Well, that's interesting.

48:57.018 --> 48:59.187
You knew the Ivans had him
all this time?

48:59.270 --> 49:01.773
I got to get out of here. Okay.

49:01.856 --> 49:03.399
Untie me right now.

49:03.483 --> 49:05.234
He's gonna kill me.

49:05.318 --> 49:06.903
He's gonna kill all of us.

49:06.986 --> 49:08.279
[Mother's Milk] Why?
What'd you do?

49:08.363 --> 49:09.906
Fuck you, all right?

49:09.989 --> 49:12.075
Let me go or we're all dead.

49:12.158 --> 49:13.826
[Butcher] Trouble
in paradise, eh?

49:13.910 --> 49:15.662
Don't you worry, darling.

49:15.745 --> 49:20.333
We got to big fish to hook,
and you're the worm.

49:20.416 --> 49:24.420
Is this a joke? Is this a joke?

49:25.463 --> 49:27.757
Come on. Let me go.

49:27.840 --> 49:30.426
Come on, guys. Let me go.

49:30.510 --> 49:32.929
- [door opens, closes]
- Come on, guys.

49:34.389 --> 49:36.557
Thanks. Here.

49:36.641 --> 49:38.226
We're sure halothane will work?

49:38.309 --> 49:39.811
Looked that way
in the Reds' video.

49:39.894 --> 49:41.270
We knock him out,
we keep him out,

49:41.354 --> 49:42.563
then we figure out
what to do with him.

49:42.647 --> 49:44.107
[Starlight] What the hell's
going on?

49:48.277 --> 49:49.946
Annie, what are you doing here?

49:50.029 --> 49:51.197
M.M. called me.

49:51.280 --> 49:53.908
- Did he?
- [Mother's Milk] Just told her

49:53.991 --> 49:55.660
we might need some backup.

49:57.120 --> 49:58.496
That's all.

49:59.872 --> 50:02.208
Look, y-you shouldn't be here,
all right? It's dangerous.

50:02.291 --> 50:03.710
It's too dangerous for me?

50:03.793 --> 50:05.795
- What about you?
- [Butcher] Oi, you lot,

50:05.878 --> 50:08.339
take your little tiff
somewhere else.

50:08.423 --> 50:09.924
We're on the job here.

50:10.007 --> 50:12.677
Okay, uh, over here. Huh?

50:15.346 --> 50:18.558
I just don't understand why
you wouldn't call me for this.

50:20.935 --> 50:24.230
Okay, okay. Look, you...
you're probably gonna be mad...

50:25.898 --> 50:28.943
...but I promised
no more secrets, right? So...

50:30.737 --> 50:33.531
Oh, my God.

50:33.614 --> 50:34.741
Hughie.

50:34.824 --> 50:36.492
Hold... One second.

50:36.576 --> 50:38.661
- You found more V?
- It's temporary V.

50:38.745 --> 50:41.164
It's temporary, okay?
I'm not an idiot.

50:41.247 --> 50:43.499
I-I know it's sketchy.
I've seen Trainspotting.

50:43.583 --> 50:45.334
But i-it's Soldier Boy.

50:45.418 --> 50:47.545
I mean, what else
was I supposed to do?

50:47.628 --> 50:50.006
- You were supposed to call me.
- Yeah, and what if you got hurt

50:50.089 --> 50:51.632
trying to save me, Annie?

50:51.716 --> 50:54.594
I would never forgive myself.
But now you don't have to, okay?

50:54.677 --> 50:58.222
I can handle myself.
I can finally save you for once.

51:00.224 --> 51:03.978
I don't need you
to save me, Hughie.

51:06.147 --> 51:07.982
I need you.

51:11.360 --> 51:13.362
[Geiger counter clicking slowly]

51:15.114 --> 51:17.116
[clicking continues faster]

51:33.382 --> 51:34.592
[grunts]

51:42.767 --> 51:44.060
[grunts]

51:44.143 --> 51:45.520
[panting]

51:45.603 --> 51:46.729
What'd you do?

51:46.813 --> 51:50.483
I know you're never
gonna forgive me,

51:50.566 --> 51:52.485
but you left me no choice.

51:52.568 --> 51:54.362
Why?

51:55.446 --> 51:57.698
I can't draw no line, M.

51:59.075 --> 52:01.202
Not with what I got to do.

52:02.829 --> 52:04.455
- [grunts]
- I'm sorry.

52:04.539 --> 52:05.581
[grunting]

52:05.665 --> 52:07.667
You'll be all right
in the morning.

52:14.048 --> 52:16.342
♪ ♪

52:30.773 --> 52:32.859
You're that asshole
from the lab.

52:33.901 --> 52:35.236
That's right.

52:35.319 --> 52:37.113
I'm the arsehole
that let you out.

52:37.196 --> 52:39.574
Russian Porta-Loos, eh?

52:39.657 --> 52:42.702
You want the Countess's head
on a spike, don't you?

52:42.785 --> 52:45.872
Well, she's in there,
yours for the taking.

52:46.914 --> 52:49.709
Consider it a gesture
of good faith.

52:49.792 --> 52:51.669
Good faith for what?

52:57.049 --> 53:00.219
I was thinking that you and I

53:00.303 --> 53:02.221
could come
to a little arrangement.

53:02.305 --> 53:05.516
What you lot call...

53:05.600 --> 53:07.018
a team up.

53:12.773 --> 53:14.191
[Crimson Countess] Ben?

53:15.234 --> 53:16.652
Is that really you?

53:22.325 --> 53:23.910
You look so young.

53:23.993 --> 53:25.578
You don't.

53:27.371 --> 53:31.000
I'm so, so sorry.

53:31.083 --> 53:33.085
It wasn't my idea.

53:33.169 --> 53:34.921
God, you got to
believe me. I-I...

53:35.004 --> 53:37.381
How much did
the Russians pay you?

53:39.383 --> 53:41.093
Hmm?

53:42.803 --> 53:44.555
They didn't.

53:44.639 --> 53:46.265
What?

53:49.644 --> 53:51.646
They didn't pay you anything?

53:55.816 --> 53:57.652
I loved you.

53:59.236 --> 54:00.655
All those years...

54:02.073 --> 54:04.992
...that they burned me

54:05.076 --> 54:08.537
and that they pumped me
full of poison,

54:08.621 --> 54:12.625
I held onto the hope
that you would come.

54:14.460 --> 54:16.671
That you would save me.

54:19.966 --> 54:21.968
Because I still loved you.

54:24.804 --> 54:26.806
I didn't love you.

54:28.015 --> 54:30.059
I hated you.

54:31.477 --> 54:33.229
We all did.

54:38.693 --> 54:41.237
[whooshing growing louder]

54:46.951 --> 54:48.077
[Hughie] Annie, please, just go.

54:48.160 --> 54:49.286
Let us handle this.
You can yell at me...

54:49.370 --> 54:51.455
[explosion]

55:11.726 --> 55:14.061
What happened? Is he hurt?

55:14.145 --> 55:16.313
Keep an eye on him.

55:16.397 --> 55:18.566
He's had four or five mgs
of Rohypnol.

55:18.649 --> 55:20.943
You fucking roofied him?!

55:22.695 --> 55:24.780
[footsteps approaching]

55:43.966 --> 55:45.176
What are you doing?

55:49.138 --> 55:50.973
[Hughie] Annie, listen.

55:51.057 --> 55:52.850
We wanted a weapon.

55:52.933 --> 55:54.643
Soldier Boy's our weapon.

55:54.727 --> 55:57.897
He's how we kill Homelander.
And Neuman maybe.

55:57.980 --> 55:59.774
If anyone's strong enough,
he is.

55:59.857 --> 56:02.276
Y-You knew Butcher
was gonna do this?

56:02.359 --> 56:05.946
M.M. never would've
gone for it, and you...

56:06.030 --> 56:08.199
- Look, you weren't
supposed to be here.
- [exhales] Oh.

56:08.282 --> 56:10.951
So...

56:11.035 --> 56:12.745
no more secrets, huh?

56:14.872 --> 56:16.957
Hughie...

56:17.041 --> 56:19.168
you're teaming up
with a murderer.

56:19.251 --> 56:22.296
This is the only way that I can
save you from Homelander.

56:24.924 --> 56:26.592
I'm doing this for you.

56:26.675 --> 56:29.428
Whatever it takes, remember?

56:31.138 --> 56:32.932
Come with us.

56:34.934 --> 56:37.561
You and me against the world.

56:37.645 --> 56:38.938
[Butcher] Hughie.

56:50.074 --> 56:51.867
Please don't go.

56:52.868 --> 56:54.870
♪ ♪

57:18.310 --> 57:20.312
♪ ♪

57:50.342 --> 57:52.344
♪ ♪

58:22.374 --> 58:24.376
♪ ♪

58:54.406 --> 58:56.408
♪ ♪

